{"tid":268744,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"夏日熱辣辣 熱辣辣","createTime":"2017-06-03T09:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T14:42:40.000Z","uid":91082,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f201a1922faa911ca77d48c2747ac5e8c90323d2","tid":268744,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"無論夏天幾熱都好，<br />\n有冇人都會用熱水沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n凍水here <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 熱到咁一定沖凍水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：沖熱水涼簡直人間天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb83f03bcbb59f2503edc252ab710c044398dc3","tid":268744,"uid":40820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:13:56.000Z","msg":"沖開滾水"},{"pid":"b51a429cde00b299f8f23b71cea116ecbdafe27b","tid":268744,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:14:22.000Z","msg":"細個睇過一集keroro話夏天用熱水沖涼，沖完會更加涼快，因為熱水令身體表面溫度高過出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以會feel到冇咁熱<br />\n利申：沖凍水"},{"pid":"ebfa50de9ca496fc2306827618bd276310483207","tid":268744,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖開滾水</blockquote><br />\n好多痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb74b58730353424c4379a650a23fbf079d63d4","tid":268744,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個睇過一集keroro話夏天用熱水沖涼，沖完會更加涼快，因為熱水令身體表面溫度高過出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以會feel到冇咁熱<br />\n利申：沖凍水</blockquote><br />\n之前聽過 <br />\n冬天游水 上咗水之後覺得凍，<br />\n係沖凍水 而唔係熱水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd5be46e77db560b9333f819a2f59e930a9ae7c","tid":268744,"uid":40820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個睇過一集keroro話夏天用熱水沖涼，沖完會更加涼快，因為熱水令身體表面溫度高過出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以會feel到冇咁熱<br />\n利申：沖凍水</blockquote><br />\nYes唔抹身既話的確係<br />\n身上嘅水珠會吸收身體嘅熱量進行evaporation<br />\n令到身體嘅能量細咗從而降溫<br />\n相反如果沖嘅水係低溫過室溫<br />\n啲能量主要係由周圍嘅環境溫度提供而唔係身體熱能<br />\n所以 沖凍水冇咁易降溫<br />\n都係因為咁所以我平時夏天沖滾水涼冬天沖冰水涼<br />\n利申：幼稚園高小英文第尾"},{"pid":"b4538fcf6505a51d2647c0d798bce1328ca73902","tid":268744,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個睇過一集keroro話夏天用熱水沖涼，沖完會更加涼快，因為熱水令身體表面溫度高過出面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以會feel到冇咁熱<br />\n利申：沖凍水</blockquote><br />\nYes唔抹身既話的確係<br />\n身上嘅水珠會吸收身體嘅熱量進行evaporation<br />\n令到身體嘅能量細咗從而降溫<br />\n相反如果沖嘅水係低溫過室溫<br />\n啲能量主要係由周圍嘅環境溫度提供而唔係身體熱能<br />\n所以 沖凍水冇咁易降溫<br />\n都係因為咁所以我平時夏天沖<span style=\"color: red;\">滾水</span>涼冬天沖<span style=\"color: teal;\">冰水</span>涼<br />\n利申：幼稚園高小英文第尾</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952affc82a1de15eff4444866d6e5ef25b37352c","tid":268744,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"沖完熱水個身抹極都唔乾<br />\n係咁出汗不如唔好沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16f956d0af2bb45cb524a141c829dd26fa1bf0e","tid":268744,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖完熱水個身抹極都唔乾<br />\n係咁出汗不如唔好沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺 沖完熱水又一身汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5507d045f67ddc28a7318bf78aef84e7a56db820","tid":268744,"uid":26680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:45:48.000Z","msg":"無論夏天定冬天都沖熱水涼"},{"pid":"e527fa9cc46b3e4f464922d10289027a6b642b61","tid":268744,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"你要吃楊枝甘露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae55dd8dea06d7627894aa669effd8cf26783dd1","tid":268744,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要吃楊枝甘露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你返去食牛肉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cdc13c0e32def9ab208ec16674b83cac471aec","tid":268744,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"芒果奶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930ba1faa402e782cdaa81b1e3cba841923874ae","tid":268744,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c33781eb07f71eb433196f6b9f77de92a372ec0","tid":268744,"uid":91082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有濕疹仲沖熱水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要唔要借眼鏡比你"},{"pid":"1b2ca1d8a9edab4f2658b82d5d0e6f69c75bf5e2","tid":268744,"uid":96007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"係呀 熱呀 熱就要跑步呀 有風呀"}]}